OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloud and
OL,6,Fshowers moving away to the southeast
OL,7,Fduring the evening. Dry and settled
OL,8,Fovernight, with clearing skies
OL,9,Fallowing temperatures to fall, feeling
OL,10,Fcold with some ground frost patches
OL,11,Fpossible. Winds light but breezy along
OL,12,Fthe coast.
OL,13,
OL,14,CSunday:FCold start Sunday, perhaps
OL,15,Ffrosty, then dry with sunny spells
OL,16,Fduring the morning before turning
OL,17,Fcloudier during the afternoon. Some
OL,18,Ffurther sunny spells late on. Winds
OL,19,Fbreezier along the coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
